			>
			<DIV></DIV>
<DIV>***Incoming Meanie Reply***</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Wizard gains are no worse of then any other class in the AA department. After the first 3 A tiers, everything is scaled down as far as Defensive and Offensive AA's are concerned.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Casters use Mana (Mental Power), Melee use endurance (Physical Power), Hybrids use both, but to a lesser extent in both fields.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I doubt there is one argument you can make that would justify Casters being able to utilize endurance for anything more then jumping while at the same time arguing against a Pure Melee being able to use Mana.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Wizards have problems, I don't think there are many out there that will disagree, but trying to get SOE to give you Disciplines is not going to make anyone take your situation seriously.</DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
